    <h1 class="hed">The Most Terrifying Thing About Ebola&nbsp;</h1>
    


 <div class="social social-with-popup sharing-buttons" id="header_social">
    <a href="#" data-share="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?s=100&p[title]=The+Most+Terrifying+Thing+About+Ebola&p[summary]=As+the+Ebola+epidemic+in+West+Africa+has+spiraled+out+of+control,+affecting+thousands+of+Liberians,+Sierra+Leonians,+and+Guineans,+and+threatening+thousands+more,+the+world&rsquo;s+reaction+has+been+glacially,+lethally+slow.+Only+in+the+past+few+weeks+have+heads+of+state+begun+to+take+serious+notice.+To+date,+the...&p[ref]=sl_live&p[images][0]=http://www.slate.com/content/dam/slate/articles/health_and_science/medical_examiner/2014/09/140919_MEDEX_EbolaPatient.jpg.CROP.thumbnail-small.jpg&p[url]=http://www.slate.com/articles/health_and_science/medical_examiner/2014/09/why_ebola_is_terrifying_and_dangerous_it_preys_on_family_caregiving_and.html?wpsrc=sh_all_dt_fb_top" class="facebook">
      <span class="icon"></span>
      <span class="count"></span>
    </a>
    <div class="twitter">
    <a href="#" data-share="http://twitter.com/share?text=The+most+terrifying+thing+about+Ebola.+It+threatens+humanity+by+preying+on+humanity.&count=none&via=slate&url=http://www.slate.com/articles/health_and_science/medical_examiner/2014/09/why_ebola_is_terrifying_and_dangerous_it_preys_on_family_caregiving_and.html?wpsrc=sh_all_dt_tw_top" class="twitter">
       <span class="icon"></span>
    </a>
    <a class="tw-count" href="http://twitter.com/search?q=http://www.slate.com/articles/health_and_science/medical_examiner/2014/09/why_ebola_is_terrifying_and_dangerous_it_preys_on_family_caregiving_and.html"><span class="count"></span></a>
    </div>
    
      <a href="#comments" class="comments">
        <span class="icon"></span>
        <span class="count"></span>
      </a>
    
 </div>


    <h2 class="dek">The disease threatens humanity by preying on humanity.</h2>
    
    <div class="byline" id="main_byline">
        By <a rel="author" href="http://www.slate.com/authors.benjamin_hale.html">Benjamin Hale</a>
    </div>
    

    





  
  
  


<div class="social horiz-counts-mobile centered sharing-buttons">
  
    <div class="comments">
      <a class="mobile-comments" href="#comments">
        <span class="icon"></span>
        <span class="count"></span>
      </a>
    </div>
  
  <div class="facebook">
    <a href="#" data-share="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?m2w&s=100&p[title]=The+Most+Terrifying+Thing+About+Ebola&p[summary]=As+the+Ebola+epidemic+in+West+Africa+has+spiraled+out+of+control,+affecting+thousands+of+Liberians,+Sierra+Leonians,+and+Guineans,+and+threatening+thousands+more,+the+world&rsquo;s+reaction+has+been+glacially,+lethally+slow.+Only+in+the+past+few+weeks+have+heads+of+state+begun+to+take+serious+notice.+To+date,+the...&p[ref]=sl_live&p[images][0]=http://www.slate.com/content/dam/slate/articles/health_and_science/medical_examiner/2014/09/140919_MEDEX_EbolaPatient.jpg.CROP.thumbnail-small.jpg&p[url]=http://www.slate.com/articles/health_and_science/medical_examiner/2014/09/why_ebola_is_terrifying_and_dangerous_it_preys_on_family_caregiving_and.html?wpsrc=sh_all_mob_fb_top" class="share facebook" target="_blank">
